@MercedesBenz unveils a new S-Class built on NVIDIA DRIVE AV which enables an L4-ready architecture.

The new S-Class with MB.OS will be equipped with NVIDIA DRIVE Hyperion architecture and full-stack NVIDIA DRIVE AV L4 software, designed to support future robotaxi operations and deliver safety-first, chauffeur-style autonomous driving, available to riders through Uber’s mobility network.

Visit the link in our bio to learn more.

